workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
This full-body session will ensure all major muscle groups have been worked on for a balanced and all-around strong body.


You'll be powering through supersets for your upper and lower body, so your lifting tempo (and the rest breaks) are critical. Lock in your form with the tutorial, then give it your all.
